bitumen insulation materials; and bitumen emulsions. It is involved in the transportation of bulk bitumen and liquefied petroleum gas; rubber processing oil; and generation of power through windmills, as well as imports and stores bitumen. The company was formerly known as Bombay Baroda Roadways (India) Limited and changed its name to Agarwal Industrial Corporation Limited in March 2008. Agarwal Industrial Corporation Limited was incorporated in 1995 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}